==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Extrication
<hw>Ex`tri*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
act or process of extricating or disentangling; a freeing from
perplexities; disentanglement.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act of sending out or evolving.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Extrinsic</ent>⟦br⟧
